{
  "stem": "23438.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We couldn't buy much on the black market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There were continuous [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] German soldiers coming to check whether we've given away all the radio sets.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And radio sets were forbidden from the [? get go. ?] There were German soldiers coming to check for guns.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We knew that our father, my father, had had a gun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But we didn't know whether he took it with him or whether he'd left it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We were terrified that they'd find it in the flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We didn't even know where to look for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Sometime later we found it, in the pocket of his coat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we just threw it out with the rubbish heap.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That first year of war, there was no school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "There was-- there were no legal high schools under the German occupation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So my mother and my aunt sort of did some schoolwork with us, as much as that was possible at home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was winter, '39, '40.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Financially, we were not all that well off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Came summer, mother organized us making ice cream and selling it through the window.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Because we lived on the ground floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And people around sort of very quickly learned that there was ice cream to be had there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And they'd come to buy it from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was great fun for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What else do I remember from those times?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Really little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had news that Father and my brother arrived in Vilna, where there was still my grandmother's family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was occupied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole east of Poland had been occupied by Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you could then correspond between the two occupation zones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew they were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
